            <tbody>
              <tr>
                <td>Table Cell 1</td>
                <td>Table Cell 2</td>
                <td>Table Cell 3</td>
                <td>Table Cell 4</td>
                <td>Table Cell 5</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>Table Cell 1</td>
                <td>Table Cell 2</td>
                <td>Table Cell 3</td>
                <td>Table Cell 4</td>
                <td>Table Cell 5</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>Table Cell 1</td>
                <td>Table Cell 2</td>
                <td>Table Cell 3</td>
                <td>Table Cell 4</td>
                <td>Table Cell 5</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>Table Cell 1</td>
                <td>Table Cell 2</td>
                <td>Table Cell 3</td>
                <td>Table Cell 4</td>
                <td>Table Cell 5</td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </article>
        <article>
          <h2 id="typography-code">Code</h2>
          <h2>Inline code</h2>
          <p><strong>Keyboard input:</strong> <kbd>Cmd+Shift+Enter</kbd></p>
          <p><strong>Inline code:</strong> <code>&lt;p&gt;paragraph&lt;/p&gt;</code></p>
          <p><strong>Sample output:</strong> <samp>Sample output from computer program</samp></p>
          <h3>Preformatted text</h3>
<pre>.ninja {
  color: black;
  visibility: hidden;
}</pre>
<pre><code>.ninja {
  color: black;
  visibility: hidden;
}</code></pre>
        </article>
        <article>
          <h2 id="typography-inline">Inline elements</h2>
          <p><a href="#!">Anchor element defines a hyperlink to a location</a></p>
          <p><strong>Strong is used to indicate strong importance</strong></p>
          <p><em>Emphasis element marks text that has stress emphasis</em></p>
          <p><b><em>B</em> element is stylistically different text from normal text</b></p>
          <p><i>Italic element is text that is offset from the normal text</i></p>
          <p><u>Underline element is text with an unarticulated, though explicitly rendered, non-textual annotation</u></p>
          <p><del>Deleted text element represents a range of text that has been deleted from a document</del></p>
          <p><ins>Inserted text elementrepresents a range of text that has been added to a document</ins></p>
          <p><s>Strikethrough element renders text with a strikethrough</s></p>
          <p>Superscript<sup>(1)</sup> element defines a span of text that should be displayed higher and often smaller</p>
          <p>Subscript<sub>(2)</sub> element defines a span of text that should be displayed lower and often smaller</p>
          <p><small>Small element makes the text font size one size smaller</small></p>
          <p><abbr title="abbreviation">Abbr.</abbr> element represents an abbreviation and optionally provides a full description for it</p>
          <p><q cite="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/q">Quote element indicates that the enclosed text is a short inline quotation</q></p>
          <p><cite>Citation element represents a reference to a creative work</cite></p>
          <p><dfn>Definition element</dfn> represents the defining instance of a term</p>
          <p><mark>Mark element represents highlighted text</mark></p>
          <p>Variable <var>var</var> element represents a variable in a mathematical expression or a programming context</p>
          <p>Time element (<time>20:00</time>) represents time on 24-hour clock, or date (<time datetime="2001-05-15T19:00">May 15</time>) in Gregorian calendar</p>
          <p><a href="#top">[Top]</a></p>
        </article>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h1 id="embedded-content">Embedded content</h1>
        <article>
          <h2 id="embedded-images">Images</h2>
          <h3>Inline image</h3>
          <p><img src="https://unsplash.it/550/350/?image=961" alt="Image"></p>
          <h3>Figure > image</h3>
          <figure><img src="https://unsplash.it/550/350/?image=961" alt="Image"></figure>
          <h3>Figure > image + figcaption</h3>
          <figure>
            <img src="https://unsplash.it/550/350/?image=961" alt="Image">
            <figcaption>Here is a caption for this image.</figcaption>
          </figure>
        </article>
        <article>
          <h2 id="embedded-audio">Audio</h2>
          <audio controls width="600">
            <source src="interlude.mp3">
            <source src="interlude.ogg">
          </audio>
        </article>
        <article>
          <h2 id="embedded-video">Video</h2>
          <video controls width="600">
            <source src="timelapse.mp4" type="video/mp4">
            <source src="timelapse.ogv" type="video/ogg">
            Your browser does not support the <code>video</code> element.
          </video>
          <h2 id="embedded-iframe">Iframe</h2>
          <iframe width="550" height="350" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/zxT0wknZxic" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>
          <h2 id="embedded-object">Object</h2>
          <object width="550" height="350" data="https://www.youtube.com/embed/zxT0wknZxic"></object>
          <h2 id="embedded-embed">Embed</h2>
          <embed width="550" height="350" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/zxT0wknZxic">
        </article>
        <article>
          <h2 id="embedded-canvas">Canvas</h2>
          <canvas id="canvas" width="550" height="350">canvas</canvas>
          <script type="application/javascript">
            (function draw() {
              var canvas = document.getElementById("canvas");
              if (canvas.getContext) {
                var ctx = canvas.getContext("2d");
                ctx.fillStyle = "rgb(230, 230, 250)";
                ctx.fillRect(0, 0, 550, 350);
                ctx.fillStyle = "rgb(200, 0, 0)";
                ctx.fillRect(20, 20, 150, 150);
                ctx.fillStyle = "rgba(0, 0, 200, 0.5)";
                ctx.fillRect(50, 50, 150, 150);
              }
            })();
          </script>
        </article>
        <article>
          <h2 id="embedded-svg">Inline SVG</h2>
          <svg width="550" height="350" viewBox="0 0 550 350" preserveAspectRatio="xMinYMin">
            <rect x="0" y="0" width="550" height="350" fill= "rgb(230, 230, 250)"/>
            <circle cx="95" cy="95" r="75" fill="rgb(200, 0, 0)"></circle>
            <circle cx="115" cy="115" r="75" fill="rgba(0, 0, 200, 0.5)"></circle>
          </svg>
        </article>
        <article>
          <h2 id="embedded-meter">Meter</h2>
          <meter value="75" min="0" max="100">2 out of 10</meter>
        </article>
        <article>
          <h2 id="embedded-progress">Progress</h2>
          <progress value="75" max="100">Progress</progress>
        </article>
        <p><a href="#top">[Top]</a></p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h1 id="forms">Forms</h1>
        <article>
          <h2>Inline</h2>
          <form>
            <p>
              <label for="input-inline-text">Label</label>
              <input id="input-inline-text" type="text" placeholder="Text field">
              <label for="input-inline-email">Label</label>
              <input id="input-inline-email" type="text" placeholder="Email field">
              <button type="submit">Button Submit</button>
            </p>
          </form>
          <h2>Justified (fieldsets)</h2>
          <form>
            <fieldset id="form-inputs">
              <legend>Input fields</legend>
              <p>
                <label for="input-text">A S D F G H J K L Z X C V B N M Q W E R T Y U I O P</label>
                <input id="input-text" type="text" placeholder="Enter your text">
                <label for="input-text">Instructions or error message</label>
              </p>
              <p>
                <label for="input-password">Password input</label>
                <input id="input-password" type="password" placeholder="Enter your password">
                <label for="input-password">Instructions or error message</label>
              </p>
              <p>
                <label for="input-url">URL input</label>
                <input id="input-url" type="url" placeholder="http://website.com">
              </p>
              <p>
                <label for="input-email">Email input</label>
                <input id="input-email" type="email" placeholder="name@email.com">
              </p>
              <p>
                <label for="input-tel">Telephone input</label>
                <input id="input-tel" type="tel" placeholder="(999) 999-9999">
              </p>
              <p>
                <label for="input-search">Search input</label>
                <input id="input-search" type="search" placeholder="Enter search term">
              </p>
              <p>
                <label for="input-number">Number input</label>
                <input id="input-number" type="number" placeholder="Enter a number">
              </p>
            </fieldset>
            <fieldset id="form-html5-inputs">
              <legend>HTML5 inputs</legend>
              <p>
                <label for="ic">Color input</label>
                <input type="color" id="ic" value="#0269c2">
              </p>
              <p>
                <label for="ir">Range input</label>
                <input type="range" id="ir" value="10">
              </p>
              <p>
                <label for="idd">Date input</label>
                <input type="date" id="idd" value="1970-01-01">
              </p>
              <p>
                <label for="it">Time input</label>
                <input type="time" id="it" value="1970-01-01">
              </p>
              <p>
                <label for="idm">Month input</label>
                <input type="month" id="idm" value="1970-01">
              </p>
              <p>
                <label for="idw">Week input</label>
                <input type="week" id="idw" value="1970-W01">
              </p>
              <p>
                <label for="idt">Datetime input</label>
                <input type="datetime" id="idt" value="1970-01-01T00:00:00Z">
              </p>
              <p>
                <label for="idtl">Datetime-local input</label>
                <input type="datetime-local" id="idtl" value="1970-01-01T00:00">
              </p>
              <p>
                <label for="if">File input</label>
                <input id="if" type="file">
              </p>
            </fieldset>
            <fieldset id="form-textarea">
              <legend>Textarea</legend>
              <p>
                <label for="textarea">Textarea</label>
                <textarea id="textarea" rows="8" cols="48" placeholder="Enter your message here"></textarea>
                <label for="textarea">Instructions or error message</label>
              </p>
            </fieldset>
            <fieldset id="form-select">
              <legend>Select</legend>
              <p>
                <label for="select">Select</label>
                <select id="select">
                  <optgroup label="Option Group">
                    <option>Option One</option>
                    <option>Option Two</option>
                    <option>Option Three</option>
                  </optgroup>
                </select>
                <label for="select">Instructions or error message</label>
              </p>
            </fieldset>
            <fieldset id="form-select-multiple">
              <legend>Select multiple</legend>
              <p>
                <label for="select-multiple">Select</label>
                <select multiple id="select-multiple">
                  <optgroup label="Option Group">
                    <option>Select multiple option one</option>
                    <option>Select multiple option two</option>
                    <option>Select multiple option three</option>
                    <option>Select multiple option four</option>
                    <option>Select multiple option five</option>
                    <option>Select multiple option six</option>
                    <option>Select multiple option seven</option>
                    <option>Select multiple option eight</option>
                  </optgroup>
                </select>
                <label for="select-multiple">Instructions or error message</label>
              </p>
            </fieldset>
            <fieldset id="form-checkboxs">
              <legend>Checkboxes</legend>
              <label for="checkbox1"><input id="checkbox1" name="group-checkbox" type="checkbox" checked="checked"> A choice is an act of selecting or making a decision when faced with two or more possibilities</label><br/>
              <label for="checkbox2"><input id="checkbox2" name="group-checkbox" type="checkbox"> A choice is an act of selecting or making a decision when faced with two or more possibilities</label><br/>
              <label for="checkbox3"><input id="checkbox3" name="group-checkbox" type="checkbox"> A choice is an act of selecting or making a decision when faced with two or more possibilities</label><br/>
            </fieldset>
            <fieldset id="form-radios">
              <legend>Radio buttons</legend>
              <label for="radio1"><input id="radio1" name="group-radio" type="radio" checked="checked"> An option is a thing that is or may be chosen</label><br/>
              <label for="radio2"><input id="radio2" name="group-radio" type="radio"> An option is a thing that is or may be chosen</label><br/>
              <label for="radio3"><input id="radio3" name="group-radio" type="radio"> An option is a thing that is or may be chosen</label><br/>
            </fieldset>
            <fieldset id="form-buttons">
              <legend>Buttons</legend>
              <p>
                Inputs
                <input type="submit" value="Input Submit">
                <input type="button" value="Input Button">
                <input type="reset" value="Input Reset">
                <input type="submit" value="Input Disabled" disabled>
              </p>
              <p>
                Buttons
                <button type="submit">Button Submit</button>
                <button type="button">Button Button</button>
                <button type="reset">Button Reset</button>
                <button type="submit" disabled>Button Disabled</button>
              </p>
            </fieldset>
          </form>
        </article>
        <p><a href="#top">[Top]</a></p>
      </section>
    </main>
